    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Catwifhat</strong> is a free-to-play idle clicker where <strong>clicking drops items and skins</strong>.</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By clicking on adorable cats in hats, every click has a chance to drop loot — including ultra-rare items with odds as low as <strong>1 in 1,000,000</strong> per click. You can play actively or leave the game running AFK and see what drops over time.</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every 3 hours, you also receive a <strong>unique cat</strong>, adding to your growing collection.</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>3 Hour Cat Drop Pool:</strong></p><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>COMMON</strong> — 70%<br></li><li><strong>UNCOMMON</strong> — 16%<br></li><li><strong>RARE</strong> — 3.5%<br></li><li><strong>EPIC</strong> — 0.499%<br></li><li><strong>LEGENDARY</strong> — 0.00099% (1 / 101,010)<br></li><li><strong>MYTHIC</strong> — 0.00001% (1 / 10,000,000)<br></li><li><strong>SPECIAL</strong> — Available during events<br></li><li><strong>LITTER BOX</strong> — 10%</li></ul><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Clicking Drop System</strong> — every click has a chance to drop items and skins<br></li><li>Idle &amp; AFK friendly — leave the game running in the background<br></li><li>Collect cats, items, talismans, cosmetics, materials, tools, and future weapon drops<br></li><li>Litter Boxes — open them with Lockpicks to receive cats and valuable items<br></li><li>Autoclickers — click for you even while AFK<br></li><li>Rewards System — claim rewards up to LVL 20 (more coming)<br></li><li>Improved visuals and redesigned UI<br></li><li>Music, click sounds &amp; adjustable audio settings</li></ul><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relax, experiment, and see what drops — or just leave it running and check back later.</p>",
